{"tid":2051141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人大䆁法代價沉重","createTime":"2020-06-04T14:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T14:24:39.000Z","uid":5281,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd372a764b09ac72b6942c9f181557071955bcca","tid":2051141,"uid":5281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"我16年前的剪報<br />\n<br />\n無話可說<br />\n<br />\n自己睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PW5G0i6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPW5G0i6.jpg&h=ae24ec29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想問16年前已經預計係咁，16年後既泛民你仲想坐喺到拎選票？35+對好多人已經係笑話！<br />\n<br />\n人地對家已經同你全面開戰，如果你地仲想玩35+，唔該你哋班人同我棟高床板諗清諗楚 多/少35+ 你地會點抗爭同點協調。<br />\n<br />\n今日64 31週年，每個人有我地必須做的事<br />\n<br />\n只要係香港人繼續不分化，不鬥黃<br />\n<br />\n和。勇。不。分<br />\n光復香港。時代革命"},{"pid":"0dcb52efabc00e7f02b67a0a85ba1d3acb45bead","tid":2051141,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:24:39.000Z","msg":"剪報撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}